        "<b>A single, over-stretched nurse:</b> one staff nurse handles emergencies — checking, referring and escorting students to the nearby hospital — and keeps a meticulous log of intake, referrals, hospital visits, receipts and prescriptions; the system is tight but clearly under-resourced, and she does not stay overnight, leaving night emergencies to (likely) a teacher.",
